---
import perfil from "../../assets/Gemini_Generated_Image_g6oiatg6oiatg6oi.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<header class="mb-20 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/90 text-on-primary-fixed text-xs text-white font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Nuestra Esencia</span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-headline font-extrabold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-8">Conoce a nuestro equipo</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary font-body leading-relaxed">
            Creamos la herramienta que nosotros mismos usaríamos para cuidar a nuestros seres queridos. Más tranquilidad.
        </p>
</header>
<section class="px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">
        <div class="card-glint delay-3 hover-lift group flex flex-col items-center md:items-start p-8 rounded-xl border-slate-100 bg-white  shadow-sm  hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="relative mb-10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 rounded-full scale-110 blur-xl group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors"></div>
                <Image 
                    alt="CTO & Partner" 
                    class="aspect-square w-55 h-55 object-cover rounded-full  border-4 border-surface-container-lowest shadow-xl  transition-all duration-500" 
                    src={perfil}
                    loading="eager"
                />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Carlos Tumbaco</h3>
                <p class="text-primary font-bold text-label-md tracking-wider uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">verified_user</span> Founder &amp; CEO
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    Con más de 15 años de experiencia en gestión hospitalaria, Carlos fundó CuidaLink con la visión de democratizar el acceso a cuidados profesionales, asegurando que cada paciente reciba atención digna en la comodidad de su casa.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <button class="p-3 rounded-full text-slate-600  hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary-fixed transition-all">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">alternate_email</span>
                </button>
                <button class="p-3 rounded-full text-slate-600  hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary-fixed transition-all">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">link</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="card-glint delay-3 hover-lift group flex flex-col md:mt-24 items-center md:items-start p-8 rounded-xl border-slate-100 bg-white  shadow-sm  hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="relative mb-10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 rounded-full scale-110 blur-xl group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors"></div>
                <Image 
                    alt="CTO & Partner" 
                    class="aspect-square w-55 h-55 object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-surface-container-lowest shadow-xl  transition-all duration-500" 
                    src={perfil}
                    loading="eager"
                />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Alonso de la Peña</h3>
                <p class="text-primary font-bold text-label-md tracking-wider uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">verified_user</span> CTO &amp; Partner
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    Con más de 15 años de experiencia en gestión hospitalaria, Alonso fundó CuidaLink con la visión de democratizar el acceso a cuidados profesionales, asegurando que cada paciente reciba atención digna en la comodidad de su casa.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <button class="p-3 rounded-full text-slate-600  hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary-fixed transition-all">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">alternate_email</span>
                </button>
                <button class="p-3 rounded-full text-slate-600  hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary-fixed transition-all">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">link</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
</section>
